              name: "Lemmings.world",
              sidebar:
                "## General\n\nA general-purpose Lemmy server that anyone can use.\n\nRead the [Code of Conduct](https://lemmings.world/post/1127) and follow the [rules](https://lemmings.world/post/1112). There's also the [new user's guide](/post/1676591).\n\nWe have a bot that travels the Fediverse and subscribes to the most popular communities, so that close to all Lemmy content gets synced here.\n\nYou can also go chat with others on our [Matrix](https://matrix.to/#/#lemmings_world:matrix.org).\n\nWe're part of the [Fediseer](https://fediseer.lemmings.world/glossary) chain of trust:\n\n![Fediseer badge showing that we're guaranteed on the Fediseer network](https://fediseer.com/api/v1/badges/guarantees/lemmings.world.svg)\n\n[![A badge showing the uptime as a percentage](https://uptime.lemmings.world/lemmings.world.svg)](https://fediverse.observer/lemmings.world)\n\n## Donations\n\nThis instance is funded out of my pocket, if you wish to donate (or just see how much it costs), visit the [donations page](https://donations.lemmings.world).\n\n## Other\n\nOther Lemmy-related things hosted on Lemmings.world:\n\n- [a.lemmings.world](https://a.lemmings.world) - the Alexandrite Lemmy frontend\n- [p.lemmings.world](https://p.lemmings.world) - the Photon Lemmy frontend\n- [old.lemmings.world](https://old.lemmings.world) - the mlmym Lemmy frontend\n- [schedule.lemmings.world](https://schedule.lemmings.world) - an app for scheduling Lemmy posts\n- [fediseer.lemmings.world](https://fediseer.lemmings.world) - a frontend for managing Fediseer",
